paint.shared.io

Class SquareTableIO

  • java.lang.Object
    • paint.shared.io.BaseTableIO
      • paint.shared.io.SquareTableIO

  • public class SquareTableIO
extends BaseTableIO
    Provides all CSV input/output operations for Square entities.

    Handles CSV reading, schema validation, entity conversion, and table appending in a consistent manner across PAINT’s square-level datasets.
